name: dogbark
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dog bark
des:
Alexa will launch a series of barks, from a standard dog bark to a howling. A random image of a dog will also appear on the screen of your device (if your device has a screen).
The random image come from a library of more than 60 images. If you are lucky you will see a wolf !
The application exits automatically at the end of the barks.

Don't hesitate to comment if you want to see images from a specific breed.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
